15:30.853 --> 15:32.146
No matter what.

15:33.773 --> 15:35.400
There's our hero.

15:36.609 --> 15:37.694
[blows kiss]

15:38.444 --> 15:39.404
Love you, Frank.

15:39.487 --> 15:41.281
Packed you a lunch, working man.

15:41.364 --> 15:42.949
Honey, I'm proud of you!

15:43.032 --> 15:46.703
We're a team, Frank.
And I need you now more than ever.

15:46.786 --> 15:49.414
You're the only person I can turn to and...

15:49.497 --> 15:51.249
[snoring]

15:51.332 --> 15:52.625
When have I ever disappointed you?

15:52.709 --> 15:54.711
Just a quick loan, honey.

15:54.794 --> 15:57.588
You can do whatever your heart desires
as long as you're home by 3:00.

15:57.672 --> 15:59.173
I'm getting a hernia supporting you.

15:59.257 --> 16:01.134
The old... [nagging sound]

16:01.217 --> 16:03.177
Blah, blah, blah!

16:03.261 --> 16:05.179
Frank, wait.

16:05.263 --> 16:09.934
Before we leave like this, is there
anything you want to say to me?

16:10.018 --> 16:11.894
Anything at all?

16:11.978 --> 16:15.919
[Pogo] That's the kind of friend I want
to be from now on, Frank.

16:16.019 --> 16:20.919
- What do you say?
- You miserable fucking asshole.

16:21.738 --> 16:23.031
Thanks a lot, fucker!

16:23.114 --> 16:27.368
- I pour my heart out to you and this is...
- No, Bob, not you! Me!

16:27.452 --> 16:29.787
Guys, I'm sorry.
I got to go see Sue.

16:29.871 --> 16:31.331
I can't do this thing with you.

16:31.414 --> 16:34.709
Can't do this?
You just did do this!

16:34.792 --> 16:36.565
Motherfucker, we just
drugged a vegetable

16:36.566 --> 16:38.338
and stuffed him in
the bottom of a plane!

16:38.421 --> 16:39.589
I know, and I'm sorry.

16:39.672 --> 16:43.092
We can't make this go away!
It's a Class-A felony.

16:43.176 --> 16:45.845
- Not in Texas.
- Hey! What y'all doing here?

16:45.928 --> 16:48.139
- Airport stuff.
- Nothing. Nothing.

16:48.222 --> 16:49.807
We were just leaving.
It's okay.

16:49.891 --> 16:53.770
No, it's not okay.
You're messing with our hijacking!

16:53.771 --> 16:56.343
[action music]
[gunshots]

16:56.378 --> 16:59.150
<i>[hijacker] Everybody put
your motherfucking hands up!</i>

16:59.233 --> 17:01.444
No, no. No, no, no, no!
You can't do this today!

17:01.527 --> 17:03.321
They're not supposed to do it
any day.

17:03.404 --> 17:07.861
If anyone asks, a Puerto Rican
put Scoop on that plane.

17:09.827 --> 17:12.329
[slurring] How did we not see that coming?

17:12.413 --> 17:14.040
We were so blind!

17:16.166 --> 17:17.335
Fucking lettuce!

17:17.417 --> 17:18.711
[grunts]

17:18.795 --> 17:20.463
Get out of the street, lady!

17:20.546 --> 17:23.549
You get out of the street, lady!

17:26.719 --> 17:30.264
That's it, Sue.
Get all those feelings out now.

17:30.348 --> 17:34.477
That way it'll be easier for you
to go back to work tomorrow.

17:34.560 --> 17:36.270
I can't go back there.

17:36.354 --> 17:38.314
That would be humiliating.

17:38.398 --> 17:41.442
Day after day,
knowing what they did to me,

17:41.526 --> 17:44.320
everybody looking at me
like I have a fatal disease.

17:44.404 --> 17:46.072
"Oh, poor Sue.

17:46.155 --> 17:48.574
They stole your idea.

17:48.658 --> 17:53.162
Now go get us some fucking ham sandwiches,
hold the mustard."

17:54.997 --> 17:58.376
Well, would your husband dying
make things better?

17:58.459 --> 18:01.879
<i>[reporter] The fifth hijacking this
week is taking place in our own backyard.</i>

18:01.963 --> 18:03.631
<i>The hijackers claim to be members</i>

18:03.714 --> 18:08.469
<i>of the Black Liberation Alliance
for Black Liberation or BLABLA.</i>

18:08.553 --> 18:10.062
Oh my God!

18:11.556 --> 18:16.394
[over PA] This is the FBI! Release those
hostages and surrender now!

18:16.477 --> 18:20.398
Fuck you! No way!
We demand $10 million

18:20.481 --> 18:23.860
to help out my forgotten
brothers and sisters in Detroit!

18:23.943 --> 18:27.330
- And Oakland!
- Sorry, man. We got to cut bait on Oakland.

18:27.365 --> 18:30.700
[whimpers]
We do not negotiate with terrorists!

18:30.701 --> 18:33.801
[guns cock]

18:34.287 --> 18:38.374
[sighs] This is why I don't come
to your fucking house on Sunday.

18:38.458 --> 18:41.419
[phone ringing]

18:41.502 --> 18:43.243
Hello?
Hey, Mom.

18:43.278 --> 18:45.590
- How'd your thing go?
- Are we millionaires now?

18:45.673 --> 18:47.300
[slurring] Your father's in danger.

18:47.383 --> 18:52.221
I need you to find somebody to drive you
to the TV store and pick me up.

18:52.305 --> 18:54.932
- Are you okay?
- I'm fine, honey!

18:57.977 --> 19:00.938
My mom's drunk
and I need a ride to go get her!

19:01.022 --> 19:02.356
Take my horse, partner.

19:04.567 --> 19:07.195
- All four hundred of them.
- Seriously?

19:07.278 --> 19:09.655
I'd drive you myself,
but giving up a gram a day

19:09.656 --> 19:12.033
of cocaine habit isn't
as easy as it sounded

19:12.116 --> 19:14.243
when I was on cocaine.

19:14.327 --> 19:16.162
[moaning]

19:17.288 --> 19:21.375
We have a bomb in this suitcase,
and we will use it!

19:21.459 --> 19:23.586
I'm the CEO of the airline.

19:23.669 --> 19:25.922
Let me talk some sense to these people.

19:26.547 --> 19:29.967
What are you fucking
animals doing on my airplane?

19:30.051 --> 19:32.470
- Mr. Dunbarton, no!
- Murphy?!

19:32.553 --> 19:36.724
What the hell are you doing here,
you shamrock-shitting pen-hoarder?

19:36.807 --> 19:40.269
- Fucking up my life, sir!
- This is your last chance.

19:40.353 --> 19:43.731
You've got ten seconds to give up
or we're storming the plane.

19:43.814 --> 19:47.948
Then you've got seven seconds before
I blow this whole place the fuck up!

19:48.444 --> 19:50.279
Well, then we'll do it in five.

19:50.363 --> 19:52.323
This ain't Name That Tune, motherfucker!

19:52.406 --> 19:55.451
I'm gonna start shooting
hostages one at a time.

19:56.327 --> 19:59.038
Go ahead. Say your prayers.

20:00.840 --> 20:04.252
- Nah, I don't think so.
- Frank, what the fuck?

20:04.335 --> 20:07.838
Buddy, if you shot me now,
you'd be doing me a favor.

20:07.922 --> 20:10.883
- My wife hates me... for good reason.
- [crowd gasps]

20:10.967 --> 20:12.969
I haven't been there for her.

20:13.052 --> 20:16.180
The only right decision I ever made
was marrying that woman.

20:16.264 --> 20:18.516
And I spent the last two months
throwing it all away.

20:18.599 --> 20:22.061
- Oh, Frank...
- Who the fuck is this guy?

20:22.144 --> 20:25.398
This morning she gave me
one last chance to fix things.

20:25.481 --> 20:27.191
I should have said I was sorry,

20:27.275 --> 20:31.320
that I think she's a great woman,
a wonderful mother,

20:31.404 --> 20:34.703
and an absolute animal in the sack.
[vomits]

20:34.740 --> 20:36.826
But I blew it.

20:36.909 --> 20:39.870
I'll tell you what.
Let all these other people go.

20:39.954 --> 20:42.206
They've actually got
something to live for.

20:42.290 --> 20:45.793
As for me?
I deserve a bullet.

20:46.711 --> 20:49.255
So, go ahead.
Just shoot me.

20:56.012 --> 20:57.680
- Frank!
- Dad!

20:57.763 --> 20:59.765
Jesus Christ!
You fucking shot me!

20:59.849 --> 21:02.727
Anybody moves,
the next one is in his head!

21:02.810 --> 21:04.228
Somebody do something!

21:04.312 --> 21:05.771
[groans]

21:05.855 --> 21:09.546
Get ready to go in. Forty percent
survival rate is acceptable.

21:09.581 --> 21:13.112
Hey! How did this plane get
in my apartment?

21:13.195 --> 21:14.655
Wha...
[grunting]

21:14.739 --> 21:17.074
- That's my nephew!
- Sweet Jesus!

21:17.158 --> 21:19.243
Those butchers are already
maiming hostages!

21:19.327 --> 21:21.245
You dirty trickers!

21:21.329 --> 21:24.332
- Gave me a sleepy coffee!
- Ah, shit.

21:24.415 --> 21:26.167
Time to call my brother-in-law.

21:26.250 --> 21:29.211
No hair dryers on the tarmac!

21:29.295 --> 21:31.631
- [man] The bomb!
- Ah!

21:32.882 --> 21:35.384
<i>[reporter] This is simply incredible.</i>

21:35.468 --> 21:38.888
<i>A courageous Mohican employee is
taking on the hijackers single-handedly.</i>

21:38.971 --> 21:42.016
<i>This is the most heroic thing
this reporter has ever seen</i>

21:42.099 --> 21:45.978
<i>since I reported on my own
reporting of the Vietnam War.</i>

21:47.940 --> 21:49.618
[chittering]

21:51.150 --> 21:52.902
Huh?

21:54.362 --> 21:55.404
[cheering]

21:57.782 --> 21:59.784
Thank you, baseball fans!

22:02.161 --> 22:06.123
Re-segregate now!
It's what white god wants!

22:06.207 --> 22:07.667
[all groan]

22:07.750 --> 22:10.294
Let's get those people off that plane!

22:10.378 --> 22:13.172
<i>- FBI!
- Keep your hands where I can see them!</i>

22:13.255 --> 22:15.508
- [Roger] Murphy!
- Ah, shit.

22:16.384 --> 22:19.261
You accidental ejaculations
thought you could

22:19.262 --> 22:22.139
get rid of my nephew by
stashing him on a plane?

22:22.223 --> 22:25.309
He's a Dunbarton!
Your genetic superior!

22:25.393 --> 22:28.687
<i>[chanting] Scoop!
Scoop! Scoop!</i>

22:28.771 --> 22:32.149
I will see you rot in a
dungeon and your children

22:32.150 --> 22:35.528
will make my underwear
in a Cambodian sweatshop!

22:35.611 --> 22:39.198
And I will wear it once,
throw it out, and demand more!

22:39.281 --> 22:41.416
[singing]
[boom, splat]

22:45.079 --> 22:46.622
Holy shit.

22:46.705 --> 22:47.832
[gasps]

22:47.915 --> 22:49.525
Mr. Dunbarton...

22:51.043 --> 22:52.920
[gurgling]

22:54.630 --> 22:56.757
Fucking idiot!

22:58.634 --> 23:00.219
Holy shit.

23:01.303 --> 23:04.098
- Holy shit!
- Sweet Jesus! [screaming]

23:05.224 --> 23:09.228
I think Dunbarton would have wanted us
to take the rest of the day off.

23:09.311 --> 23:11.230
- Frank!
- Sue?

23:12.374 --> 23:15.278
[music]

23:15.313 --> 23:17.736
- Ah!
- Oh, my God! Are you okay?

23:17.820 --> 23:20.114
I'll be fine.
It went right through.

23:20.197 --> 23:21.449
And I did kind of ask for it.

23:21.532 --> 23:24.076
I know. I heard everything you said.

23:24.160 --> 23:27.371
Oh. Yeah, I don't think
I was making a whole lot of sense.

23:27.455 --> 23:30.833
I knew exactly what you meant.
And it was beautiful.

23:30.916 --> 23:32.084
- Daddy!
- Dad!

23:32.168 --> 23:34.420
Hey, guys!
I'm sorry you kids had to see that.

23:34.503 --> 23:36.881
Yeah, that was really fucked up.

23:36.964 --> 23:38.507
Yes, it was.

23:38.591 --> 23:40.468
And it's gonna hurt for a while.

23:40.551 --> 23:42.261
But here's how you deal with it:

23:42.344 --> 23:43.679
