24:17.713 --> 24:18.881
Yes, it is.

24:18.964 --> 24:20.925
That old broad didn't deserve you.

24:21.008 --> 24:23.177
Your next invention will be even better.

24:23.260 --> 24:27.556
Whatever you want to do,
I will support you one thousand percent.

24:27.640 --> 24:29.808
Thank you, sweetie.

24:30.768 --> 24:34.063
