24:54.208 --> 24:57.545
Frank, it feels like
we have a chance at a new start.

24:57.628 --> 25:00.756
The kids are getting older now and
they're not gonna need us as much anymore.

25:00.839 --> 25:02.800
You could go back to college.

25:02.883 --> 25:04.718
And you could take flight lessons.

25:04.802 --> 25:06.512
Maybe I will.

25:06.595 --> 25:08.514
Come here, beautiful.

25:11.809 --> 25:14.687
- Oh, Frank.
- Latex, my dear?

25:14.770 --> 25:17.189
